main event: Two unidentified objects connected by a dark body were observed at Grenier AFB on August 3, 1953.
interesting points: The objects were described as spherical and connected by a dark unidentified body between them., One of the objects was larger than the other., The sighting lasted for about 5 minutes., The speed, size, and course of the objects were unknown., The case was evaluated as insufficient data, with a possibility that it could be a balloon with a payload.
sighted object: two spherical objects connected by a dark body
